the district planning committee is the only constitutionally mandated planning body in india not even the plng cmsn niti aayog or the state planning boards as it is the state of integrated planning in the country has been a non starter despite of all the efforts taken during the upa regime however bodies like niti aayog state planning commissions are still provided with resources and manpower so that they are able to take crucial decisions but when the question comes of empowering the dpc and enthusing the dpc members to perform as per the act theapathy of the government is clearly visible with utter confusion lack of any credible information and parallel orders the most critical level of planning where there is a possibility of merging the rural and urban sector plans and ensuring the rural urban continuum ensuring convergence of schemes and programmes of the line departments and avoiding duplication prioritising local level needs is being neglected and subverted by adhoc and politically motivated actions its high time to walk the talk and allow dpcs to function with autonomy and necessary resources for effective integrated district planning implementation and monitoring

acha muje portray stories pasand hein jaise vietnam war in fact next month tho mein maya lin se milne vala tha mein uska war memorial ka kaam designing

oh ye kafi involved lagta hai saara scandal kafi interesting lag raha hai kya tumhe historical dramas ache nahi lagte
han editor katharine graham ko pata tha ki usey decide karna padega ki isey publish karein ya nahi agar wo karegi wo contempt of the court ke liye charge ho sakti hai aur agar wo publish karegi to wo washington post ko importan joturnalistic institution ki tarah establish karta hai
wo newspaper ki heir thi to wo usko apni family legacy samajhti thi
gosh aisa lagta hai jaise history never changes government always trying to silence the press

accha hai for them

kya company kuch patent ya legal documents ki hifazat me hai
main nahi jaanta par zukerbreg ko college database ko hack karne aur harward computer network ko crash karne ke liye 6 months ka academic probation mila tha so wo is baat se aware hoge ki rogue programmer kis prakar ka damage kar sakte hai
as a programmer me ye dekh sakta hun ki databases aur networks me hacking se jo nuksaan ho sakta hai
damage is situation me hone ke liye bounded tha
